language Essence 1.3

given v: int(1..)
given b: int(1..)
given r: int(1..)
given k: int(1..)
given lambda: int(1..)
find design: function (total) int(1..v) --> set (size r) of int(1..b)
such that
    and([sum([toInt(block in design(point)) | point : int(1..v)]) = k | block : int(1..b)]),
    and([and([sum([toInt(block in design(p1) /\ block in design(p2)) | block : int(1..b)]) = lambda
                  | p2 : int(p1 + 1..v)])
             | p1 : int(1..v)])

